            loc="novel1_letter4_chapter5_p163__Start"/&gt;“And <seg xml:id="C11_app268-fThomas_end"/>
            <seg type="invariant-MissingWit" xml:id="C11_app269-fThomas_start"/>now I must tell you a little <seg xml:id="C11_app269-fThomas_end"/>
